an Alphabet''\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|lessac, frane|[[Fran\u00e9 Lessac]]}}\n|<!-- Illustrator --> {{sort|lessac, frane|[[Fran\u00e9 Lessac]]}}\n|<!-- Publisher --> [[William Morrow & Company]]\n|<!-- Citation --> Commended\n|- \n|<!-- Year --> 1994\n|<!-- Title --> ''Cool Salsa: Bilingual Poems on Growing Up Latino in the United States''\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|Carlson, Lori marie|Lori Marie Carlson}} (ed.)\n|<!-- Illustrator --> \n|<!-- Publisher --> [[Henry Holt and Company]]\n|<!-- Citation --> Commended\n|- \n|<!-- Year --> 1994\n|<!-- Title --> {{sort|day's work|''A Day's Work''}}\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|bunting, eve|[[Eve Bunting]]}}\n|<!-- Illustrator --> {{sort|himler, ronald|Ronald Himler}}\n|<!-- Publisher --> [[Clarion Books]]\n|<!-- Citation --> Commended\n|- \n|<!-- Year --> 1994\n|<!-- Title --> ''De Colores and Other Latin American Folksongs for Children''\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|Orozco, Jose-Luis |[[Jose-Luis Orozco]]}}\n|<!-- Illustrator --> {{sort|Kleven, Elisa |[[Elisa Kleven]]}}\n|<!-- Publisher --> [[Dutton Books]]\n|<!-- Citation --> Commended\n|- \n|<!-- Year --> 1994\n|<!-- Title --> ''Feliz Nochebuena, Feliz Navidad''\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|Presilla, Maricel E. |[[Maricel Presilla|Maricel E. Presilla]]}}\n|<!-- Illustrator --> {{sort|Espinosa Ferrer, Ismael |Ismael Espinosa Ferrer}}\n|<!-- Publisher --> [[Henry Holt and Company]]\n|<!-- Citation --> Commended\n|- \n|<!-- Year --> 1994\n|<!-- Title --> {{sort|las nanas de abuelita|''Las nanas de abuelita / Grandmother's Nursery Rhymes''}}\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|Palacio Jaramillo, Nelly |Nelly Palacio Jaramillo}}\n|<!-- Illustrator --> {{sort|Savadier, Elivia |Elivia Savadier}}\n|<!-- Publisher --> [[Henry Holt and Company]]\n|<!-- Citation --> Commended\n|- \n|<!-- Year --> 1994\n|<!-- Title --> ''How Music Came to the World: An Ancient Mexican Myth''\n|<!-- Author --> {{sort|Ober, Hal |Hal Ober}}\n|<!-- Illustrator --> {{sort|Ober, Carol |Carol Ober}}\n|<!-- Publisher --> [[Houghton